"><div class="media-object-interactiveLink"><div class="image-container"> <a class="interactive-link" href="https://www.wsj.com/articles/from-one-cell-review-biology-science-blueprints-for-building-b4c74d17"><img width="16" height="10" src="https://images.wsj.net/im-834080?width=700&amp;height=467" alt="不明确的" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><span class="image-interactive-icon">
            </span></a></div><div class="wsj-article-caption"><span class="wsj-article-credit">科学图片库/盖蒂图片社</span></div></div></div><p>基因中映射的指令到底是如何创建多细胞生命令人眼花缭乱的复杂三维结构的呢？<em>阿德里安·沃尔夫森评论</em></p><p><a href="https://www.wsj.com/articles/from-one-cell-review-biology-science-blueprints-for-building-b4c74d17?mod=article_inline" target="_blank" class="icon none">阅读评论</a></p><div class="media-object scope-web|mobileapps
          smallrule
"><div class="wsj-article-page-rule"></div></div><h3> <a href="https://www.wsj.com/articles/cosmic-scholar-review-harry-smiths-strange-frequencies-8558cc53?mod=article_inline" target="_blank" class="icon none">《宇宙学者》评论：<strong>哈利·史密斯的奇怪频率</strong></a></h3><div class="media-object scope-
          inline
