            </span></a></div><div class="wsj-article-caption"><span class="wsj-article-credit">海·赫什/哈利·史密斯档案</span></div></div></div><p>史密斯收集了善本、纸飞机、宾夕法尼亚荷兰语工具，并收获了改变一代人的民间音乐唱片。<em>蒂莫西·法林顿评论</em></p><p><a href="https://www.wsj.com/articles/cosmic-scholar-review-harry-smiths-strange-frequencies-8558cc53?mod=article_inline" target="_blank" class="icon none">阅读评论</a></p><div class="media-object scope-web|mobileapps
